---
// ToastNotification.astro
// Auto-hiding toast shown when a nav link is clicked (disappears after 3s)
---

<div
  id="toast-notification"
  class="fixed bottom-5 right-5 bg-atlantis-900 text-white py-3 px-5 rounded-lg shadow-lg opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 z-50"
>
  <p>Loading link...</p>
</div>
